Rare Special Items.name: ★ Falchion Knife | Stained
Rare Special Items.desc: It has been given a forced patina using lemon and mustard dripped onto the surface.
Rare Special Items.lore: If you think it's messy now, wait until you see it under a blacklight

Rare Special Items.name: ★ Falchion Knife | Urban Masked
Rare Special Items.desc: It has been spray-painted using a tangle of masking tape as a stencil.
Rare Special Items.lore: True power is demonstrated with subtle application

Rare Special Items.name: ★ Falchion Knife | Blue Steel
Rare Special Items.lore: This is the malbec of weapon design - Booth, Arms Dealer

Rare Special Items.name: ★ Falchion Knife | Slaughter
Rare Special Items.desc: It has been painted in a zebra-stripe pattern with aluminum and chrome paints with various reflectivities, and has then been covered with a tomato red candy coat.
Rare Special Items.lore: Valeria doesn't pay Javier to ask questions... she pays him to pry out answers

Rare Special Items.name: ★ Falchion Knife | Scorched
Rare Special Items.desc: It has been spray-painted in a sun-dappled pattern.
Rare Special Items.lore: The Phoenix is not a symbol of destruction... it's a symbol of rebirth - Valeria Jenner, Revolutionary

Rare Special Items.name: ★ Falchion Knife | Safari Mesh
Rare Special Items.desc: It has been spray-painted using mesh fencing and cardboard cutouts as stencils.
Rare Special Items.lore: A predator is a predator, no matter the environment

Rare Special Items.name: ★ Falchion Knife | Case Hardened
Rare Special Items.desc: It has been color case-hardened through the application of wood charcoal at high temperatures.
Rare Special Items.lore: A little color never hurt anyone

Rare Special Items.name: ★ Falchion Knife | Fade
Rare Special Items.desc: It has been painted by airbrushing transparent paints that fade together over a chrome base coat.
Rare Special Items.lore: This isn't just a weapon, it's a conversation piece - Imogen, Arms Dealer In Training

Rare Special Items.name: ★ Falchion Knife | Crimson Web
Rare Special Items.desc: It has been painted using a spider web-patterned hydrographic over a red base coat and finished with a semi-gloss topcoat.
Rare Special Items.lore: Be careful where you walk, you never know where the web is spread

Rare Special Items.name: ★ Falchion Knife | Forest DDPAT
Rare Special Items.desc: It has been painted using a Digital Disruptive Pattern (DDPAT) hydrographic.
Rare Special Items.lore: By the time you're close enough to notice the pixels it's already too late

Rare Special Items.name: ★ Falchion Knife | Boreal Forest
Rare Special Items.desc: It has been painted using a forest camouflage hydrographic.
Rare Special Items.lore: The woods can be a dangerous place... never travel alone

Rare Special Items.name: ★ Falchion Knife | Night
Rare Special Items.desc: It has individual parts spray-painted solid colors in a night ops color scheme.
Rare Special Items.lore: It's the whisper of the wind... it's the bite at your neck

Covert Skins.name: AWP | Hyper Beast
Covert Skins.desc: It has been custom painted with a beastly creature in psychadelic colours.
Covert Skins.lore: You really want to impress me Booth? Make this black light sensitive - Rona Sabri, Rising Star

Covert Skins.name: AK-47 | Aquamarine Revenge
Covert Skins.desc: It has been custom painted with the image of a pod of dolphins.
Covert Skins.lore: Is there an echo in here?

Classified Skins.name: SG 553 | Cyrex
Classified Skins.desc: It has been custom painted with a high-tech design in black, white, and red.

Classified Skins.name: CZ75-Auto | Yellow Jacket
Classified Skins.desc: It has been custom painted with curved shapes.
Classified Skins.lore: Float like a butterfly, sting like a relentless hateful insect

Classified Skins.name: MP7 | Nemesis
Classified Skins.desc: It has been custom painted with the image of a metallic monster.

Restricted Skins.name: M4A4 | Evil Daimyo
Restricted Skins.desc: It has been custom painted with a graphic design in red and black.
Restricted Skins.lore: Carmen. I found him...- The Oni and The Valkyrie Part 1

Restricted Skins.name: FAMAS | Neural Net
Restricted Skins.desc: It has been painted with a translucent hydrographic over a metallic base coat.
Restricted Skins.lore: I know. But it was the right thing to do... - A Family Affair Part 2

Restricted Skins.name: Negev | Loudmouth
Restricted Skins.desc: It has been custom painted with a monstrous design and then distressed.
Restricted Skins.lore: Get back here, I'm talking to you!

Restricted Skins.name: MP9 | Ruby Poison Dart
Restricted Skins.desc: It has been painted with red and purple metallic paints over a black base coat.
Restricted Skins.lore: Who says diamonds are a girl's best friend?

Restricted Skins.name: P2000 | Handgun
Restricted Skins.desc: It has been custom painted with a hand making an aiming gesture.

Mil-Spec Skins.name: Galil AR | Rocket Pop
Mil-Spec Skins.desc: It has been custom painted with a graphic design of stripes and pixellated particles.
Mil-Spec Skins.lore: The perfect thing for a hot summer's day

Mil-Spec Skins.name: Nova | Ranger
Mil-Spec Skins.desc: It has been painted with a brush stroke hydrographic and detailed with heat-transfer decals.

Mil-Spec Skins.name: P90 | Elite Build
Mil-Spec Skins.desc: It has been custom painted using a combination of hydrographics and careful stenciling and detailed with heat-transfer decals.
Mil-Spec Skins.lore: Tread softly Naomi...people in your line of work aren't known for their longevity - The Shield and The Serpent Part 2

Mil-Spec Skins.name: UMP-45 | Riot
Mil-Spec Skins.desc: It has been painted using a combination of hydrographics and heat-transfer decals.
Mil-Spec Skins.lore: If you didn't want collateral damage, perhaps you should have been more specific... - Javier Alviso, Fist of the Phoenix

Mil-Spec Skins.name: Glock-18 | Bunsen Burner
Mil-Spec Skins.desc: It has been given a blue patina which has been polished off parts of the slide to result in a graphic flame design.

Mil-Spec Skins.name: USP-S | Torque
Mil-Spec Skins.desc: It has been custom painted in a modern black, white and yellow design.
Mil-Spec Skins.lore: They're manipulating you Kotaro. And if you can't see that, you're in more trouble than you know... - Felix Riley, Commanding Officer
